## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5d15e-102">Le applicazioni utilizzano il riconoscimento condiviso per accedere il riconoscimento vocale di Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5d15e-102">Applications use the shared recognizer to access Windows Speech Recognition.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5d15e-103">Usare il <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> oggetto da aggiungere per l'esperienza utente vocale di Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5d15e-103">Use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> object to add to the Windows speech user experience.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5d15e-104">Questa classe consente di controllare vari aspetti del processo di riconoscimento vocale:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5d15e-104">This class provides control over various aspects of the speech recognition process:</span></span>  
  
